---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SectionDetail from "../../components/astroComponents/SectionDetail.astro";
import GetInTouchForm from "../../components/reactComponents/GetInTouchForm";
---
<BaseLayout>
    <SectionDetail title="IT support, governance and cybersecurity">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto ">
            <p class="text-base">
                We design, build, and manage robust IT environments that strengthen business continuity, safeguard
                assets, and drive operational efficiency. </p>
            <ul class="text-xl space-y-5 mt-4 list-disc pl-6 list-outside">
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">IT Services & Cybersecurity Solutions
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">We deliver flexible, scalable IT and cybersecurity solutions—whether
                        you're
                        building foundational infrastructure, enhancing your security posture, or optimizing cloud and
                        mobile operations.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Network Security Architecture & Threat Protection
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">Our end-to-end network security solutions help protect your systems, data,
                        and
                        communications from evolving cyber threats—ensuring a resilient and compliant IT environment.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Mobile Device Management (MDM) & Endpoint Security
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">We provide centralized control and security over mobile endpoints—enabling
                        secure, seamless operations and reducing vulnerabilities across your mobile workforce.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">VoIP Communication Systems & Unified Communications
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">Our advanced VoIP solutions streamline internal and external
                        communication—offering reliable, cost-effective voice services tailored to your operational
                        needs.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">24/7 IT Infrastructure Monitoring & Alerting
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">We deliver around-the-clock monitoring and performance visibility—helping
                        you
                        detect and resolve IT issues proactively to reduce downtime and maintain operational stability.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Server Infrastructure Management & Maintenance
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base"> Our proactive server support ensures optimal system
                        performance—minimizing
                        disruptions and extending the lifespan of your critical IT assets.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Virtualization & Scalable Cloud Infrastructure Solutions
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">We help you optimize resource utilization and scale operations
                        efficiently—through virtualization strategies that enhance agility, reduce costs, and simplify
                        infrastructure management.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Data Backup, Recovery & Business Continuity Solutions
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base"> Our secure data backup and disaster recovery services ensure your
                        critical
                        business data is protected, recoverable, and resilient in the face of system failures or
                        cyberattacks.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Active Directory & Enterprise Email Services
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base"> We manage Active Directory Domain Services and enterprise-grade email
                        systems—streamlining user access, strengthening authentication, and improving communication
                        security across your organization.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Cloud Computing Strategy, Migration & Management
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base"> Our cloud experts help you design, migrate, and manage scalable cloud
                        environments—empowering your business with flexibility, performance, and innovation.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Hardware Installation & Lifecycle Support
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">We provide professional setup and maintenance of IT hardware—from
                        workstations
                        to servers—ensuring reliable operation, quick deployment, and minimal downtime.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Database Administration & Optimization Services
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base"> Our comprehensive database management solutions ensure your critical data
                        systems remain secure, accessible, and high-performing—supporting decision-making and
                        operations.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h2 class="font-bold">Comprehensive Cybersecurity & Risk Management
                </h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">We deliver advanced cybersecurity services—ranging from threat detection
                        and
                        vulnerability management to incident response and security framework development—to fully
                        protect your IT ecosystem.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h2 class="font-bold">Ready to Strengthen Your IT Infrastructure & Cybersecurity Capabilities?</h2>
                    <p class="pl-4 text-base">Whether you're modernizing legacy systems or building a secure digital
                        foundation,
                        our expert services deliver protection, scalability, and operational impact.
                        <strong class="font-bold">Get in touch </strong> today to discover how we can support your IT
                        transformation journey.
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </SectionDetail>
</BaseLayout>